PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Fisheries and Oceans of certain persons as directors of the Board of Directors of the Freshwater Fish Marketing Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years. (Sam Murdock, Koostatak, Manitoba, in the place of Raymond James Fleming, whose term has expired; and William Dysart, South Indian Lake, Manitoba, in the place of Claudette Bourrier, whose term has expired)
